[Rabies is almost always a fatal disease in humans and animals. But
it is very preventable in pets with a simple vaccine. It is generally
preventable in people, by exercising some caution around bats and
wild animals. - Mod.TG

The species of bat is not given.
Photo of skunk:
<http://fohn.net/skunk-pictures-facts/skunk-images/Skunk-in-Grass-800x600.jpg>
There was no human exposure to the skunks reported here. - Mod.JW]

